"<p>6.</p><p>We talked over the phone for a while<br/>Every now and again we needed something familiar<br/>and I guess we supposed that we'd do</p><p>Eventually, you realized that we were making a mistake<br/>and you stopped answering my calls<br/>I kept calling.</p><p>I grew accustomed to the familiar beep<br/>of your answering machine<br/>I didn't know if you even listened to my messages</p><p>and I didn't care.</p>"